SUMMARY:Information: MILDMAY LINE: From 1930 Saturday 14 until 1200 Sunday 
 15 March\, no service between Shepherds Bush and Willesden Junction. 
 SOUTHERN services will not operate between Shepherds Bush and Watford 
 Junction from 2000 Saturday until 1200 Sunday. Last trains are at 1851 
 Stratford to Clapham Junction (1932 at Willesden Junction) and at 1949 
 from Clapham Junction to Stratford. First trains on Sunday are at 1123 
 from Stratford to Clapham Junction (1203 from Willesden Junction) and at 
 1159 from Clapham Junction to Stratford.
